evisum (0.6.6-1) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Add network in/out tracking (Linux only).
  * Update process list and process view.
  * Massive preparatory work undertaken to prepare for evisum 2.0.
  * Fix IPC code.
  * Fix invalid use of EDC (strdup/stringshare).
  * Rework the animator on the about window.
  * Add support for network transfer per-process (Linux).
  * Create our own widget “exel”.
  * Tidy up the other cpu visuals.
  * Use evas_vg and vectors for our graphs.
  * Add disk i/o tracking (Linux only).
  * Fix process view window resize so it remembers.
  * Columns in widget can reorder.
  * Fix column header names to be concise like the others.

 -- Robert Wiley <ylee@bodhilinux.com>  Sat, 04 Apr 2026 05:19:42 -0400

